of national champion statoil and a robust system of governance that could curb statoil's excesses as needed at a few key junctures norway's evolving champion statoil and the politics of state enterprise national oil companies search news everything news of interest pesd releases study of nigeria's national oil company nnpc september 10 2010 announcement national treasure mexico's problems with its state run oil company show why supply is so tight david g victor newsweek on april 17 2008 pesd releases case study of pemex mexico's national oil company april 17 2008 news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
